   - Log:
     - All XRDisplaySubsystem instances and running states.
   - Confirm:
     - You see anything (even just a cube in VR‑clear).
     - XRDisplaySubsystem.running == true.

If this scene works:

- Your XR configuration + OpenXR + Meta Quest Support are fundamentally sound.
- Any remaining issues are in your runtime bootstrap logic, not the platform.

If this scene still shows a dark grey frame:

- The problem is below your code:
  - OpenXR feature sets,
  - Meta Quest Support,
  - Activity/manifest,
  - or plugin conflicts.

